parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PPS can cause the front passenger airbag to not deploy in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury to the passenger.
symptoms: Airbag warning light comes on
passenger airbag sensor failure
PPS assembly shorted internally
internal electronic performance issues
preload failure region 1
communication fault
and faulty passenger side seat sensor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of recall parts can lead to a delay in repairing the vehicle, leaving the driver and passengers at risk of injury due to the faulty PPS system.
symptoms: Dealership unable to obtain recall parts
parts on backorder
no estimated time of arrival for parts
and recall repair not completed due to parts unavailability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes when the engine is cold can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when driving in heavy traffic or on steep inclines.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to stop or slow down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power while driving, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power while driving
the ignition switch feels loose or stuck
the vehicle's electrical systems malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to malfunction or not deploy in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the passenger airbag light says "off" when someone is seated or unseated
the airbag system malfunctions
the airbag does not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger presence sensor can cause the passenger airbag to malfunction or not deploy in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the passenger airbag light says "off" when someone is seated or unseated
the passenger presence sensor malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delays in repairing recalled vehicles can increase the risk of accidents or injuries due to the underlying defects.
symptoms: Dealerships are unable to repair recalled vehicles due to parts unavailability
dealerships are unresponsive or unhelpful
owners are unable to get loaner vehicles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The key getting stuck in the ignition can cause the vehicle to be unable to start or move, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The key gets stuck in the ignition
the key cannot be removed unless the manual button under the steering wheel is pushed and pulled simultaneously.
